achievements.title: Legacy
achievements.subtitle: We have been operating in Georgia's healthcare industry for more than 15 years. Continuous development and ongoing improvement across all areas of our work are essential to us, strengthening our position as a reliable and qualified partner of the medical field.
achievements.employeesDescription: An unprecedented number of employees and a distinctive organizational management approach in the market.
achievements.partnersDescription: Constant communication and support with leading global medical brands and manufacturers.
achievements.customersDescription: Numerous satisfied local clients and successfully completed projects.

testimonials.title: Testimonials
testimonials.subtitle: Across Georgia, Medic has initiated numerous successful projects, strengthening our position and helping us build long-term partnerships with representatives of the medical field.
